      <title>由于电动汽车持续疲软，欧洲 3 月份汽车销量下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/europe-car-sales-drop-in-march-as-ev-weakness-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于大众汽车公司和 Stellantis NV 等汽车制造商面临需求疲软，尤其是电动汽车需求疲软，3 月份欧洲乘用车销量下降 2.8%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/europe-car-sales-drop-in-march-as-ev-weakness-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
